{"tid":2162232,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"專一好男人認真想喺連登尋求高質絲打(靈魂伴侶)","createTime":"2020-08-18T04:22:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-18T04:49:38.000Z","uid":1627,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"19afd1197a9b3e9157f5ae24fdf5b0d99905c934","tid":2162232,"uid":1627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T04:22:03.000Z","msg":"今年28歲，asso畢業，月入14k，識中文同少量日文(少量，真係少量，都係睇片自學)，英文唔可以話差，起碼都識講句thank you<br />\n雖然我搵既錢唔多，但絕對唔少，1個禮拜食2-3次譚仔都冇乜問題，m記間中都會加大，同我一齊絕對唔會餓親你<br />\n屋企有兩老，仲有個30幾歲既阿哥，不過佢日日都喺屋企訓，最多都係去樓下返幾個鐘ok咁，而家我地住緊間舊公屋，好感受到家庭既溫暖，我最憎就係私樓撚，完全離曬地又冇人情味<br />\n我平時除咗返工就係上下連登，打下機咁，覺得自己過得好充實，生活都幾多姿多彩<br />\n我感情狀態a0.5，曾經同一個小學同學曖昧過，但最後都冇結果，之後就冇鍾意過人，因為我要搵靈魂伴侶，唔係啲隨隨便便既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇絲打有興趣同我一齊互相了解下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有意就tg me：hugo1991"},{"pid":"d6352e806cb72f8c83b60afdb478104b19d5dad2","tid":2162232,"uid":1627,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T04:22:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e68242f2ffafcd1f5dabb5e9ed57d15dbb451341","tid":2162232,"uid":4787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T04:23:01.000Z","msg":"Pmed"},{"pid":"9f64e74ec782badb72b150c84421225eb3f29e78","tid":2162232,"uid":1627,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e68242f2ffafcd1f5dabb5e9ed57d15dbb451341","tid":2162232,"uid":4787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T04:23:01.000Z","msg":"Pmed"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T04:23:18.000Z","msg":"非gay，thx"},{"pid":"e35519d41fe23415044ac8b6b6004bdd6a6d64c3","tid":2162232,"uid":1627,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T04:24:12.000Z","msg":"尋求絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希